three%20reasons%20the%20asset%20class%20isn't%20ideal%20for%20investors%20right%20now%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Col%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EIt's%20interest-rate%20sensitive%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EIt's%20easy%20to%20tax%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EIt's%20a%20nailed-down%20asset%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Fol%3E%3Cp%3EFrom%20Dalio's%20perspective%2C%20the%20first%20reason%20seems%20to%20be%20the%20most%20important.%20%26quot%3BReal%20estate%20is%20more%20interest%20rate%20sensitive%20than%20it%20is%20inflation%20sensitive%2C%20so%20given%20our%20current%20circumstances%20it%20is%20likely%20to%20go%20down%20in%20real%20terms%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20second%2C%20Dalio%20noted%20that%20because%20real%20estate%20is%20an%20asset%20that%20can%20be%20taxed%20easily%2C%20the%20holder's%20ability%20to%20diversify%20can%20be%20limited%2C%20which%20can%20compromise%20them%20financially.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20third%20reason%20on%20Dalio's%20short%20list%20may%20concern%20investors%20who%20believe%20worse%20times%20are%20coming.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BReal%20estate%20is%20nailed%20down%2C%20so%20investing%20in%20it%20makes%20it%20more%20difficult%20to%20move%20money%20from%20one%20place%20to%20another%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20highlighting%20a%20course%20of%20action%20that%20people%20often%20take%20when%20economic%20circumstances%20appear%20grim.%20Real%20estate%2C%20unlike%20stocks%20or%20other%20assets%2C%20is%20very%20illiquid%2C%20and%20it%20can%20be%20difficult%20for%20investors%20to%20get%20their%20money%20out%20of%20a%20property%20if%20they%20need%20cash%20quickly.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDalio's%20conservative%20advice%20on%20real%20estate%20investing%20related%20closely%20to%20other%20strategies%20he's%20outlined%20for%20weathering%20a%20US%20debt%20spiral.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fray-dalio-national-debt-crisis-investing-strategy-inflation-gold-bitcoin-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EDalio%20said%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20an%20event%20in%20July%20that%20the%20most%20important%20things%20one%20can%20do%20are%20to%20hedge%20portfolios%20against%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstagflation-recession-us-economy-inflation-unemployment-outlook-apollo-torsten-slok-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_self%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Einflation%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20diversify%20holdings.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fray-dalio-gold-bitcoin-allocation-investing-us-debt-crisis-deficit-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ealso%20suggested%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20investors%20should%20consider%20allocating%2015%25%20of%20their%20portfolio%20for%20either%20gold%20or%20bitcoin%20to%20protect%20against%20economic%20risks%2C%20although%20he%20said%20he%20prefers%20gold%20over%20crypto.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20July%2C%20Dalio%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-debt-crisis-ray-dalio-economy-deficit-gdp-interest-rate-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emade%20it%20clear%20%3C%2Fa%3Ethat%20he%20believes%20the%20US%20is%20running%20out%20of%20time%20to%20take%20action%20that%20could%20help%20it%20avert%20economic%20disaster.%20Reducing%20the%20deficit%20is%20possible%20but%20not%20likely%2C%20leading%20him%20to%20raise%20grave%20concerns%20about%20the%20direction%20of%20the%20US%20economy.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20the%20US%20doesn't%20cut%20the%20deficit%20to%203%25%20of%20the%20GDP%2C%20and%20soon%2C%20we%20risk%20facing%20an%20economic%20heart%20attack%20in%20the%20next%20three%20years.%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20in%20July.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freal-estate-investing-advice-ray-dalio-taxes-inflation-debt-crisis-2025-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1755008393000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2F