an%20AI-shaped%20job%20market.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20told%20BI%20that%20a%20third%20of%20their%20curriculum%20should%20focus%20on%20using%20and%20overseeing%20AI%20systems.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EA%20third%20of%20college%20teaching%20should%20be%20about%20how%20to%20use%20AI%20and%20understand%20its%20limits%2C%20a%20leading%20economist%20has%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETyler%20Cowen%2C%20a%20professor%20at%20George%20Mason%20University%2C%20previously%20warned%20that%20universities%20were%20%26quot%3Bproducing%20a%20generation%20of%20students%20who%20will%20go%20out%20on%20the%20labor%20market%20and%20be%20quite%20unprepared%20for%20what%20they're%20expected%20to%20do%26quot%3B%20as%20AI%20reshapes%20the%20world%20of%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAsked%20what%20colleges%20should%20do%20instead%2C%20Cowen%20told%20Business%20Insider%20there%20should%20be%20a%20%26quot%3Bhuge%20change.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20we%20should%20devote%20up%20to%20one-third%20of%20the%20curriculum%20to%20teaching%20students%20how%20to%20use%2C%20interact%20with%2C%20and%20spot%20the%20limitations%20of%20AIs%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-college-students-use-ai-homework-study-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ehigher%20education%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20students%20%26quot%3Bare%20taught%20many%20things%20that%20the%20AI%20does%20very%20well%2C%20such%20as%20answering%20routine%20questions%20about%20routine%20areas%20of%20knowledge%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20a%20problem%2C%20he%20said%2C%20because%20%26quot%3Bthis%20is%20in%20fact%20quite%20a%20large%20part%20of%20the%20curriculum.%20We%20teach%20things%20that%20are%20easy%20to%20test%20for.%20That%20is%20exactly%20what%20the%20AIs%20tend%20to%20excel%20at.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSome%20of%20that%20education%20still%20may%20be%20needed%20so%20that%20people%20can%20interact%20with%20the%20AI%20appropriately%2C%20but%20there%20is%20no%20point%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fenglish-teacher-my-students-relying-on-ai-for-everything-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eteaching%20skills%3C%2Fa%3E%20where%20the%20machine%20outcompetes%20the%20human%2C%26quot%3B%20Cowen%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECowen%20said%20that%20colleges%20need%20to%20rethink%20what%20and%20how%20they%20teach%20to%20prepare%20students%20for%20the%20future%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fadvice-on-how-to-land-big-tech-ai-job-education-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ejob%20market%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECowen%20said%20there%20were%20already%20categories%20of%20work%20that%20AI%20is%20disrupting%2C%20such%20as%20routine%20service%20jobs%2C%20especially%20those%20done%20behind%20a%20computer%2C%20like%20customer%20service%2C%20processing%20work%2C%20and%20IT%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECowen%20said%2C%20whatever%20human%20oversight%20is%20still%20needed%2C%20the%20%26quot%3Bamount%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-impact-unemployment-job-loss-young-tech-workers-goldman-sachs-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ehuman%20labor%3C%2Fa%3E%20required%20in%20these%20areas%20will%2C%20over%20time%2C%20fall%20dramatically.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECowen%20previously%20said%20he%20wasn't%20confident%20institutions%20were%20ready%20to%20shift%20teaching%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-reveals-how-broken-our-education-system-is-economist-says-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etoward%20mentorship%20and%20critical%20thinking%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20ability%20to%20reshuffle%20the%20personnel%2C%20the%20procedures%2C%20we%20just%20seem%20to%20me%20really%20quite%20frozen%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20podcaster%20Azeem%20Azhar%20in%20July.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ae2c303c-1490-4aeb-859b-6589c9196a2e%5C%22%3ECowen%20previously%20warn