ght%20it%20could%20happen.%20Life%20has%20a%20funny%20way%20of%20giving%20you%20a%20second%20chance.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20with%206.8%20million%20followers%2C%20Varsha%20is%20living%20proof%20that%20an%20undying%20passion%20can%20take%20you%20to%20places%20you%20never%20even%20imagined.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Arunava%20Banerjee%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1754994600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Ffeatured-img-21_11zon-1751008510-300x157.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D485427%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Born%20into%20poverty%2C%20Varsha%20Solanki%20worked%20as%20a%20domestic%20help%20while%20nurturing%20a%20lifelong%20passion%20for%20dance.%20After%20marriage%20and%20motherhood%2C%20she%20turned%20to%20social%20media%20to%20rekindle%20her%20art%2C%20going%20viral%20and%20reaching%20five%20million%20followers.%20Here's%20her%20story.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Khushi%20Arora%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F485427%2Fvarsha-solanki-dance-instagram-journey%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Think%20before%20you%20comment%20in%20UAE%3A%20Posting%20negative%20comments%20online%20can%20cost%20you%20AED%20500%2C000%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1754994435000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-123256670%2Cimgsize-53304.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fthink-before-you-comment-in-uae-posting-negative-comments-online-can-cost-you-aed-500000%2Farticleshow%2F123251101.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F123251101.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EThe%20UAE%20is%20intensifying%20its%20enforcement%20of%20cyb