%99ve%20completely%20cut%20children%20off%20from%20the%20source%20%E2%80%94%20the%20Earth%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDetermined%20to%20bridge%20this%20gap%2C%20Pragati%20began%20experimenting%20with%20her%20terrace%20garden.%20%E2%80%9CI%20wanted%20Neel%20to%20understand%20why%20he%20needed%20to%20eat%20vegetables%20%E2%80%94%20not%20just%20as%20something%20on%20his%20plate%2C%20but%20as%20living%20things%20that%20grow%20from%20the%20Earth%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20cultivated%20over%2035%20varieties%20of%20fruits%2C%20vegetables%2C%20and%20herbs%2C%20absorbing%20herself%20in%20organic%20farming%2C%20permaculture%2C%20and%20sustainable%20practices.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20deepen%20her%20understanding%2C%20she%20completed%20a%20diploma%20in%20organic%20farming%20from%20Indira%20Gandhi%20National%20Open%20University%20(IGNOU)%20in%202015%2C%20along%20with%20several%20other%20courses%20in%20farming%20and%20sustainability.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20important%20for%20me%20to%20learn%20thoroughly%20so%20I%20could%20teach%20other%20children%20and%20make%20the%20process%20meaningful%2C%20not%20just%20a%20hobby%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EGrowing%20knowledge%3A%20From%20a%20terrace%20garden%20to%20a%20citywide%20mission%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20small%20experiment%20blossomed%20into%20a%20larger%20vision%E2%80%94to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F435817%2Fkerala-woman-grows-organic-exotic-vegetables-fruits-spices-beekeeping-poultry%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eintroduce%20farming%20and%20sustainability%3C%2Fa%3E%20education%20in%20schools%2C%20with%20a%20special%20focus%20on%20government%20institutions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2F